Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:10.68,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.37,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.83,0:00:38.65,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In a certain world,\Nwhere magic is everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.73,0:00:43.35,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and Yuno were abandoned \Non the same day at
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.35,0:00:46.30,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,a church in the village of Hage, \Nwhich lies in the boonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.30,0:00:50.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They both dreamed of becoming the Wizard \NKing, the highest rank among mages,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:53.53,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and worked hard every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.01,0:00:57.95,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In the year they turned fifteen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:01:01.37,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,they both received grimoires,\Nwhich enhance the owner's magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:04.50,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They then took the Magic Knights \NEntrance Exam to join
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:07.21,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the Magic Knights, which are \Nled by the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:12.92,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see who can become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.73,0:01:18.39,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, because Yuno possesses \Nimmense magical powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.39,0:01:22.06,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,out of the nine squads, he chose \Nthe elite Golden Dawn to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:24.27,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,As for Asta, who had no magical powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:27.98,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,he ended up joining the squad \Nof rogues, the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:32.82,main,ASta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still going to become \Nthe Wizard King someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:42.47,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Thus the two finally took the first step \Ntoward becoming the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:02:01.14,main,Farmer,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:22.97,main,Farmer,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:38.36,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, there's trouble. An anomaly—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:40.05,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,An anomaly has occurred, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:47.62,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Let's have them work on this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:49.29,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:11.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I would always close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:16.01,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And cower at reality
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:20.77,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:25.23,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Of just making excuses to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:26.10,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be near you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:28.35,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Any minute now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:31.94,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:31.94,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(The decisive battle is still a long way off)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.10,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Black and blue
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:39.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give up on giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:43.16,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And get the world on my side
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:46.83,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the reason I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:52.16,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time somewhere under this sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:58.18,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Break through the tearful nights
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:01.47,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And head where the light shines
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:05.30,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep my promise
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:08.85,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:12.82,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,shape of love
