Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:44.81,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:48.84,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,What's Mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.97,0:22:48.84,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What's Mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.32,0:22:52.40,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, do you know what mana is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.40,0:22:53.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:55.14,sign_32916_371_Mana,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(355,1)}Mana
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.49,0:22:55.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's written like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:22:57.35,sign_32971_372_Mana,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Mana
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:57.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's written with the same \Ncharacter for "magic"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:22:59.58,sign_33024_375_Serious_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,244)}Serious
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.88,0:23:00.19,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,These both mean "serious"!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:05.82,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Mana is a powerful energy \Nthat exists in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.13,0:23:09.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! And everyone has it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.20,0:23:11.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Except me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.36,0:23:16.45,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Mages use up their mana to use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:18.43,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That's why if they run out of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.43,0:23:21.46,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,they might not be able to use \Nmagic again until they recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.87,0:23:22.96,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:24.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:29.02,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What a lovely flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.02,0:23:32.30,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect for giving to a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.30,0:23:33.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:36.00,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're so aggressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:37.88,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I've never met a flower like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:42.44,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You've got really powerful magic, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:46.40,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight with everything \Nwe have, to the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:50.91,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 15:\N"The Diamond Mage."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:55.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 15\N\N{\fs18}The Diamond Mage
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.91,0:23:53.74,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is my magic.
